The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Robot as a teacher

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: In an innovative step taken to improve the standard of table tennis in the city, a table tennis robot will be inaugurated at the Bijoynagar Club in Naihati on Sunday. 

This will be the third of its kind in the state. 

The robot is enabled to play with the players and help them upgrade the standards of the game. 

